title: In search of Sunrise Compilation Series By DJ Tiesto & Richa
description:
This is one of the longest running and most successful compilation series with 7 volumes from non-other than DJ Tiesto and last two volumes from Dutch trance sensation Richard Durand. This series contains some breathtaking mixes from top producers in the world. Some classics from tiesto himself produced before he changed his style to mostly house oriented electronic music. 

For All true trance lovers.

Download & Enjoy...
Seed as long as you can... :)
